            "retina": true,
            "title": "The Fit",
            "text": "<p>Choosing the fit for your ring is crucial, think about how you are wearing it and what you are wearing it with. Do you need a court band, something more modern such as a flat top and how heavy do you need it to be? </p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
