            "retina": true,
            "title": "The Style",
            "text": "<p>There are so many styles of wedding rings, but starting with the right base is key. Are you keeping is simple and going for a seamless plain band, or are you looking for something with a bit of glitter and adding some diamonds or gemstones in. </p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_J4JtgN": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image_full_width": false,
            "image_link": "",
            "retina": true,
            "title": "The Shape",
            "text": "<p>For most gents rings a straight band is all that is needed, however for those who are fitting a wedding ring next to an engagement ring you may well need a shaped band. We work closely with you to find  a pre made fit or bespoke a peice which fits perfectly to your exisiting ring. </p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_XJ6XU3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image_full_width": false,
            "image_link": "",
            "retina": true,
            "title": "The Finish",
            "text": "<p>The final piece of the puzzle is deciding the finish of your ring. Are you looking for a high polish or would you prefer a softer satin touch. You might even want some patterns across your piece with some mixed metals to highlight the design. We can finish your ring and add some personalisation via engraving if that is what you like. </p>",
            "link_label": "",
